title: Pre-existing type errors in billing test and workbench files
issue: Multiple type errors exist in the codebase that block `pnpm typecheck` from passing: 1) route.test.ts has 9 instances of 'stripe is possibly null' (TS18047) at lines 112, 121, 153, 195, 200, 248, 278, 306, 311. 2) workbench-client.tsx has missing RecordingSettings properties (rna_timeout_seconds, max_call_duration_minutes) at line 38.
suggestion: For route.test.ts: Add null checks or assertions for stripe variable. For workbench-client.tsx: Add the missing required properties rna_timeout_seconds and max_call_duration_minutes to the RecordingSettings object.
